  "detailed_description": "<br><br>Explore A Massive City<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/99bc0ca9f01d2f33a9c2ee4c6f269626.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Start illegal businesses<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/be0804bdd2340fc97751ff352dc9d701.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Ship your product<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/e0ce17478b2ba1b6fd05d7f68da57b42.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Mine for resources<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/adf0ee7af6cfb0f18de3bd66959182d7.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br><br><br>Greed of man is an open world MMO RPG where you start from the bottom fighting enemies and mining resources. Eventually you can conquer areas of the map with the people in your lobby to unlock rewards. You can progress through many different aspects of the game including Mining, Combat, Farming, Foraging, Fishing, and Scuba Diving. You can collect rare items and sell them on the market for a hefty profit. Try to become the richest in the game! After all, it is Greed of Man.",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br>Explore A Massive City<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/99bc0ca9f01d2f33a9c2ee4c6f269626.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Start illegal businesses<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/be0804bdd2340fc97751ff352dc9d701.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Ship your product<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/e0ce17478b2ba1b6fd05d7f68da57b42.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br>Mine for resources<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336720/extras/adf0ee7af6cfb0f18de3bd66959182d7.avif?t=1720120535\" width=616 height=180 /></span><br><br><br><br>Greed of man is an open world MMO RPG where you start from the bottom fighting enemies and mining resources. Eventually you can conquer areas of the map with the people in your lobby to unlock rewards. You can progress through many different aspects of the game including Mining, Combat, Farming, Foraging, Fishing, and Scuba Diving. You can collect rare items and sell them on the market for a hefty profit. Try to become the richest in the game! After all, it is Greed of Man.",
